<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister Confirms Citizenship of Paul Ames </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Minister Confirms Citizenship of Paul Ames </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA1205021294 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 in Spanish 0000 GMT 12 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1205021294 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
