<H3> <TI>   Study Predicts 1994 Budget Deficit of $15 Billion </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Study Predicts 1994 Budget Deficit of $15 Billion </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY1005034394 Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL in Portuguese 7 
May 94 p 10 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PY1005034394 </F>
<F P=104>  Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL </F>
<F P=105>  Portuguese </F>


