<H3> <TI>   Failure To Achieve Constitutional Reform Scored </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Failure To Achieve Constitutional Reform Scored </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94SM0345D Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL in Portuguese 23 
Apr 94 p 2--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

