<H3> <TI>   Concludes Visit to Brazil </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Concludes Visit to Brazil </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA1205160094 Havana PRENSA LATINA in Spanish 1119 GMT 12 May 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

