<H3> <TI>   Budapest Mayor Seeks Cooperation With Havana </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Budapest Mayor Seeks Cooperation With Havana </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL1105201894 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1700 
GMT 11 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL1105201894 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Rebelde Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


