<H3> <TI>   Conditions for Seizure of Illegally Gained Wealth Set </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Conditions for Seizure of Illegally Gained Wealth Set </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL1205231694 Havana Cuba Vision Network in Spanish 2220 GMT 
12 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL1205231694 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Cuba Vision Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Sources from the Cuban Attorney General's Office 
have announced that conditions have been created to implement 
Decree-Law 149 nationwide by means of which legal action will be 
taken in cases of illegal accumulation of wealth. 
Representatives from the Office of the Attorney General and the 
public administration in every province will move against 
hoarders by seizing their ill-gotten goods while confiscation, 
which will be determined by the Finance and Prices Ministry, is 
in process. 
  This launches a unique and vigorous endeavor that gives 
continuity to the collective efforts of the revolutionary 
process to preserve social discipline. Official sources have 
announced that the population will be informed in a timely 
manner of the fulfillment of this measure. 

</TEXT>

