<H3> <TI>   Bank President on Parallel Currency Market </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bank President on Parallel Currency Market </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA1205232594 Caracas Radio Nacional de Venezuela Canal 
Clasico Network in Spanish 2200 GMT 10 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1205232594 </F>
<F P=104>  Caracas Radio Nacional de Venezuela Canal 
