the military are not fulfilling the functions of federal 
policemen, like controlling and issuing passports. 
  Civil Household Chief Henrique Hargreaves said government 
action is not against the strike, but against disorder and 
indiscipline. Hargreaves added that their demand for salary 
parity with those of civil policemen is illegal. 

</TEXT>

