<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Congress Authorizes UN Troop Deployment to Mozambique </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY1405011994 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network in Portuguese 
2200 GMT 13 May 94 </F>

